text: I mean, you're maybe not wrong, even if your logic is flawed lol
I get you hun. There ARE definitely good, valid reasons to have no desire for your partner. It's awfully hard to want to fuck someone who acts like a piece of shit.
This is part of why I've finally felt motivated to go to the gym actually. I want to work on me, and find satisfaction in that, since my love life isn't doing it for me.
